219403039431335", "locale": "es_ES", "screenshots": [{"file_name": "39031554_1741370576635170_9153857022625467847_n.png", "id": "778732097618892", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75404232_778732100952225_2884315308028983113_n.png?_nc_cat=101&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=XpMVbjweV3EQ7kNvgGdv5hz&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&_nc_gid=AnT34mrarna3bhvM-PrQ108&oh=00_AYBBx-8abiGDPNAW0OPIOmJLzwdcGlTzpKzc8VDgKIWP0g&oe=66F540D8"}, {"file_name": "75223475_1162823078097533_7582761299006264209_n.png", "id": "456975673615142", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75644996_456975676948475_1501049188434088250_n.png?_nc_cat=109&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=IuDBKKo1bG4Q7kNvgEznarH&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&_nc_gid=AnT34mrarna3bhvM-PrQ108&oh=00_AYBSYJtyoyahpQsBvAV6C6BCF-oRyLN-MnqPdYhhx2XgeA&oe=66F56094"}, {"file_name": "38974844_895662389267965_6947818508336999764_n.png", "id": "1406277873367538", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39035315_1406277876700871_7644795770220401427_n.png?_nc_cat=103&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=8Ipqay9MtqEQ7kNvgF2162i&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&_nc_gid=AnT34mrarna3bhvM-PrQ108&oh=00_AYDBVSpFGuxP7LVlSV2btyQsBun77KAnJG4GvzLrAB6k3A&oe=66F53343"}, {"file_name": "75303836_779859827464952_3382793253436204291_n.png", "id": "1434464947071164", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39031551_1434464950404497_3647210872812083270_n.png?_nc_cat=107&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=7u_3EFlU0_4Q7kNvgFC8MVI&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&_nc_gid=AnT34mrarna3bhvM-PrQ108&oh=00_AYAJTbCB7hJMYSGJu5i3JdnGERC15H2LG1ILJU3TZA9Qog&oe=66F53E0E"}, {"file_name": "38974573_323217870728505_2789591530293209412_n.png", "id": "3657710414477901", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974468_3657710417811234_5340372445666123440_n.png?_nc_cat=100&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=wITCZoNr2hAQ7kNvgGPenm7&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&_nc_gid=AnT34mrarna3bhvM-PrQ108&oh=00_AYC_Y5R7QPZ9cReq164vPojNDi5NG1pnhS7MzfZjYlucfQ&oe=66F561C2"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": {"file_name": "75422387_1144260340145670_3292770953071563569_n.png", "id": "1178660033326518", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974650_1178660036659851_5772260596551159468_n.png?_nc_cat=104&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=g1uVEGZmXuYQ7kNvgHp9VBi&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&_nc_gid=AnT34mrarna3bhvM-PrQ108&oh=00_AYCtDNxh-8lw4h6RtMwZwplKCjKPvHGSTHDdAfByiMYBCQ&oe=66F5526F"}, "display_name": "AURORA Lite", "keywords": [], "long_description": "Con AURORA puedes validar tus proyectos 3D benefici\u00e1ndote de las ventajas que te ofrece hacerlo un entorno virtual:\n\n\u2705 identifica previamente los problemas en el dise\u00f1o.\n\u2705 visualizan distintos acabados del producto final.\n\u2705 minimiza la necesidad de contar con prototipos f\u00edsicos.\n\u2705 ahorra en costes y tiempo durante tus procesos.\n\n\u00a1Es muy f\u00e1cil e intuitivo de usar! Una vez hayas importado tu modelo 3D, sum\u00e9rgete en un escenario y empieza a validar tu proyecto.\n\nTienes a tu disposici\u00f3n un kit completo de herramientas con las que puedes: \n\u25cf seccionar el modelo 3D\n\u25cf desmontar por piezas,\n\u25cf visualizar los acabados\n\u25cf tomar anotaciones\n\u25cf realizar mediciones\n\n\u00a1Solicita tu demo gratuita y pru\u00e9balo durante 30 d\u00edas!", "short_description": "AURORA es un software de Realidad Virtual que te permite analizar y manipular tus proyectos 3D de manera inmersiva.\n\n\u00a1Importa tu modelo, elige tu escenario y comienza a validar!\n\nGracias a sus intuitivas herramientas puedes seccionar el modelo 3D, desmontar por piezas, realizar ajustes, cambiar los materiales, visualizar los acabados, tomar anotaciones y mediciones... \u00a1y mucho m\u00e1s!"}, {"images": {"nodes": [{"file_name": "AURORA_Cover-Landscape_2560x1440px.png", "id": "1832983900556697", "image_type": "APP_IMG_COVER_LANDSCAPE", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75262747_1832983903890030_2704860775782661962_n.png?_nc_cat=104&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=CaHPhwPNX1sQ7kNvgFPanzs&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&_nc_gid=AnT34mrarna3bhvM-PrQ108&oh=00_AYAbyt00l_Zho1RtpRnt0MCXbgUHfjNuIc1z9KHui8fwIw&oe=66F56478"}, {"file_name": "AURORA_Cover-portrait_1008x1440px.png", "id": "1478431766115370", "image_type": "APP_IMG_COVER_PORTRAIT", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75572758_1478431769448703_935245602461316142_n.png?_nc_cat=107&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=vndHc_0NTRkQ7kNvgGVJW67&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&_nc_gid=AnT34mrarna3bhvM-PrQ108&oh=00_AYAjVHAUJS_jTGdCof4KLFnOo20VC_zjPPkVWYx5d9DYxQ&oe=66F54124"}, {"file_name": "AURORA_Cover-square_1440x1440px.png", "id": "1005727894504726", "image_type": "APP_IMG_COVER_SQUARE", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974689_1005727897838059_2929393393789319802_n.png?_nc_cat=103&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=YLyuqKxcWL0Q7kNvgG8ZY5p&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&_nc_gid=AnT34mrarna3bhvM-PrQ108&oh=00_AYB61ME4G8oI_Xw1G_8rTLp5fiWjFreXvjqiUTT5qEn1_A&oe=66F54F26"}, {"file_name": "AURORA_Cover-minilandscape_1080x360px.png", "id": "785874000394449", "image_type": "APP_IMG_SMALL_LANDSCAPE", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75411996_785874003727782_7038698344156280861_n.png?_nc_cat=102&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=K3SQ_f1a45cQ7kNvgGU7-wd&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&_nc_gid=AnT34mrarna3bhvM-PrQ108&oh=00_AYC37NoXk4cVXNJAQIDTwPvceAOyN3GZON60ZmajDX7s4Q&oe=66F560FA"}, {"file_name": "AURORA_Icon-512x512px.png", "id": "512196221131353", "image_type": "APP_IMG_ICON", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75404232_512196224464686_7404951702432032362_n.png?_nc_cat=104&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=7BoMyLwaQvwQ7kNvgFlc2OR&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&_nc_gid=AnT34mrarna3bhvM-PrQ108&oh=00_AYBe09eJIXcOPgSXr5eSKtQnOtjAb6XkYUAjyCLdSnaCCQ&oe=66F53BB1"}, {"file_name": "AURORA_Hero-cover_3000x900px.png", "id": "438462589150660", "image_ty